public static enum Relay.XbeeDigitalIOPin
extends java.lang.Enum<Relay.XbeeDigitalIOPin>

Represents the Xbee digital IO pin that is used to monitor the status of this relay.

See http://code.google.com/p/xbee-api/wiki/XBeePins for what these mean.

Author:
